Interface FileUploadListener

public interface FileUploadListener
extends ResponseListener

Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when Box.upload() is called.

onProgress

void onProgress(long bytesTransferredCumulative)
Called periodically during upload so you can monitor upload progress.

Parameters:
bytesTransferredCumulative - The number of bytes transferred so far. Note that this will eventually slightly exceed the size of the file being uploaded because of overhead of HTTP requests (e.g. HTTP headers)
